                <h2 id="c1">​Terms and Conditions of Hotel Reviews & Posting</h2>
                <p>You agree to post reviews and contributions in accordance with the following terms and conditions (“the Terms”). LateRooms reserves the right to vary the Terms from time to time and the Terms published at the time of browsing shall be those in effect.</p>
                <h3>Hotel Reviews</h3>
                <p>
                    Only the opinions of a person, or people, who have actually stayed at the hotel(s) concerned may be submitted. You must accept all liability for the contents of all postings made by you, or on your behalf.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Please be aware that the hotel which you review will receive a preview of your comments 2 days prior to them appearing on the website. The hotelier may request your booking reference number in order to address your comments. In some circumstances this may affect your anonymity, but only with regard to the hotel you are reviewing. Your review may be withheld for up to fourteen days while LateRooms vet your comments prior to posting.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We will review all submissions for basic profanities and vulgar language and we reserve the right to remove (or not publish) comments at our discretion. We also reserve the right to identify you in response to a court order, threat of legal action or complaint.
                </p>
                <p>
                    If you believe that there is a review on LateRooms.com that should be removed due to the fact that it may offend or be illegal, please let us know and we will investigate and take action if appropriate.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Please be advised that any review that you post on LateRooms.com may be shared across all websites operated by Late Rooms Ltd and may be distributed to selected LateRooms partner websites.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Please be aware the name and location you choose in the reviews form will be displayed alongside your review.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Any review submitted by, or on behalf of you, must not:
                </p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Make any comment that is inappropriate, using defamatory, vulgar, obscene or abusive language.
                    </li>
                    <li>Send or transmit any file that may contain viruses or any material that could in any way harm another person’s computer.
                    </li>
                    <li>Contain any advertising.
                    </li>
                    <li>Disclose somebody’s personal identity or details.
                    </li>
                    <li>Contain any illegal material or material that you are not authorised to submit.
                    </li>
                </ol>
                <p>
                    Contributors under the age of 18 should get the permission of a parent or guardian before submitting any review or contribution.
                </p>
                <p><a href="#top">Back to the top</a></p>
